            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "زَكَاةِ اَلْفِطْرَةِ أَ يَصْلُحُ أَنْ يُعْطَى اَلْجِيرَانُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "اَلظُّئُورَةُ مِمَّنْ لاَ يَعْرِفُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " وَ "
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "لاَ يَنْصِبُ"
          },
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": " فَقَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:2:37:17",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/37/17",
      "text": [
        " «لاَ بَأْسَ بِذَلِكَ إِذَا كَانَ مُحْتَاجاً »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2077 - Ali ibn Yaqtin asked Imam Abu Al-Hasan Al-Awwal (as) about Zakat al-Fitr:\n\"Is it permissible to give it to neighbors or close acquaintances who do not share the same beliefs or who do not acknowledge (the Imamate)?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"There is no harm in that if they are in need.\""
        ]
      }
    },
